"{\"uid\": \"aljazeera.com-opinions-2024-7-26-what-to-watch-for-at-paris-2024-olympics-reusable-cups\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"In the spirit of the Olympics, it's time for all of us to come together and ditch single-use plastic in favour of reuse.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 120, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the spirit\", \"from\": 3, \"to\": 13}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 17, \"to\": 29}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 36, \"to\": 40}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 52, \"to\": 54}, {\"ngram\": \"single-use plastic\", \"from\": 82, \"to\": 100}, {\"ngram\": \"favour\", \"from\": 104, \"to\": 110}, {\"ngram\": \"reuse\", \"from\": 114, \"to\": 119}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Director of Strategic Initiatives for Oceana.\", \"from\": 122, \"to\": 167, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 160, \"end\": 166, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polyenso\", \"score\": 0.9999998783546363, \"rank\": 1.216424335733781e-07, \"text\": \"Oceana\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polyenso\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Polyenso\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Director\", \"from\": 122, \"to\": 130}, {\"ngram\": \"Strategic Initiatives\", \"from\": 134, \"to\": 155}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Save Share The 2024 Olympic Games are upon us and like many people around the world, I am excited to tune in and follow the action.\", \"from\": 169, \"to\": 302, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 2024 Olympic Games\", \"from\": 180, \"to\": 202}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 212, \"to\": 214}, {\"ngram\": \"many people\", \"from\": 224, \"to\": 235}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 243, \"to\": 252}, {\"ngram\": \"tune\", \"from\": 270, \"to\": 274}, {\"ngram\": \"the action\", \"from\": 289, \"to\": 299}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like most, I will cheer for athletes from my home country.\", \"from\": 303, \"to\": 361, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 331, \"to\": 339}, {\"ngram\": \"my home country\", \"from\": 345, \"to\": 360}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not wanting to miss the moments when new world records are set and stars are made, I will watch the sprinting.\", \"from\": 362, \"to\": 472, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the moments\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 393}, {\"ngram\": \"new world records\", \"from\": 399, \"to\": 416}, {\"ngram\": \"stars\", \"from\": 429, \"to\": 434}, {\"ngram\": \"the sprinting\", \"from\": 458, \"to\": 471}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a marine scientist, I have a natural affinity with anything remotely related to the ocean so I will also likely follow all the watersports.\", \"from\": 473, \"to\": 615, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a marine scientist\", \"from\": 476, \"to\": 494}, {\"ngram\": \"a natural affinity\", \"from\": 503, \"to\": 521}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 527, \"to\": 535}, {\"ngram\": \"the ocean\", \"from\": 556, \"to\": 565}, {\"ngram\": \"all the watersports\", \"from\": 595, \"to\": 614}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Finally, over the next two weeks, I will be tuning in across all events to watch for something most will not notice - reusable cups.\", \"from\": 616, \"to\": 748, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the next two weeks\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 648}, {\"ngram\": \"all events\", \"from\": 677, \"to\": 687}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 710}, {\"ngram\": \"reusable cups\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 747}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For a living, I campaign to stop plastic pollution from devastating our oceans.\", \"from\": 750, \"to\": 829, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a living\", \"from\": 754, \"to\": 762}, {\"ngram\": \"plastic pollution\", \"from\": 783, \"to\": 800}, {\"ngram\": \"our oceans\", \"from\": 818, \"to\": 828}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As part of this work, my colleagues and I are trying to get the world's largest beverage companies to sell more of their drinks in reusable packaging instead of single-use plastic.\", \"from\": 830, \"to\": 1010, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 833, \"to\": 837}, {\"ngram\": \"this work\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 850}, {\"ngram\": \"my colleagues\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 865}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's largest beverage companies\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 928}, {\"ngram\": \"their drinks\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 957}, {\"ngram\": \"reusable packaging\", \"from\": 961, \"to\": 979}, {\"ngram\": \"single-use plastic\", \"from\": 991, \"to\": 1009}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A 10 percent increase in reusable beverage packaging globally by 2030 caneliminatemore than one trillion single-use plastic bottles and cups and prevent up to 153 billion of these containers from polluting the world's waterways and seas.\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1248, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A 10 percent increase\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1032}, {\"ngram\": \"reusable beverage packaging\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1063}, {\"ngram\": \"one trillion single-use plastic bottles\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1142}, {\"ngram\": \"cups\", \"from\": 1147, \"to\": 1151}, {\"ngram\": \"these containers\", \"from\": 1185, \"to\": 1201}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's waterways\", \"from\": 1217, \"to\": 1238}, {\"ngram\": \"seas\", \"from\": 1243, \"to\": 1247}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reusable packaging is the best solution the beverage industry has for addressing its contribution to the plastic pollution crisis currently facing our oceans.\", \"from\": 1249, \"to\": 1407, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Reusable packaging\", \"from\": 1249, \"to\": 1267}, {\"ngram\": \"the best solution\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1288}, {\"ngram\": \"the beverage industry\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1310}, {\"ngram\": \"its contribution\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1346}, {\"ngram\": \"the plastic pollution crisis\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1378}, {\"ngram\": \"our oceans\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1406}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For six years running, Coca-Cola and Pepsi have been named among theworld's top plastic pollutersby the international Break Free From Plastic movement.\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1559, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1431, \"end\": 1440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coca-Cola\", \"score\": 0.9999999999295142, \"rank\": 7.060090080687544e-11, \"text\": \"Coca-Cola\", \"types\": [\"Q2095\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coca-Cola\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coca-Cola\"}, {\"begin\": 1445, \"end\": 1450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pepsi\", \"score\": 0.645692064075091, \"rank\": 0.5487258642904542, \"text\": \"Pepsi\", \"types\": [\"Q2095\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pepsi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pepsi\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"six years\", \"from\": 1412, \"to\": 1421}, {\"ngram\": \"theworld's top plastic\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1495}, {\"ngram\": \"the international Break\", \"from\": 1508, \"to\": 1531}, {\"ngram\": \"Plastic movement\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1558}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, I was thrilled when I first learned that the Paris 2024 Olympic and Paralympic Games would serve beverages to spectators inreusable packaging, potentially replacing millions of single-use plastic cups.\", \"from\": 1560, \"to\": 1765, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1609, \"end\": 1619, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1030552200753655e-15, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1632, \"end\": 1648, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999999386091, \"rank\": 3.4090637194099044e-11, \"text\": \"Paralympic Games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"beverages\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1670}, {\"ngram\": \"spectators\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1684}, {\"ngram\": \"packaging\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1705}, {\"ngram\": \"millions\", \"from\": 1729, \"to\": 1737}, {\"ngram\": \"single-use plastic cups\", \"from\": 1741, \"to\": 1764}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This decision by Paris 2024 is an important milestone in the global fight against plastic pollution, marking a shift towards large-scale reuse systems and away from the take-make-waste economy where packaging is used only once, then discarded.\", \"from\": 1767, \"to\": 2010, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1784, \"end\": 1794, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1030552200753655e-15, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This decision\", \"from\": 1767, \"to\": 1780}, {\"ngram\": \"an important milestone\", \"from\": 1798, \"to\": 1820}, {\"ngram\": \"the global fight\", \"from\": 1824, \"to\": 1840}, {\"ngram\": \"plastic pollution\", \"from\": 1849, \"to\": 1866}, {\"ngram\": \"a shift\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 1883}, {\"ngram\": \"large-scale reuse systems\", \"from\": 1892, \"to\": 1917}, {\"ngram\": \"the take-make-waste economy\", \"from\": 1932, \"to\": 1959}, {\"ngram\": \"packaging\", \"from\": 1966, \"to\": 1975}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2024 Games will be the largest sporting event in history to use reusable packaging, thoughrecent reportshave indicated that this effort will be less than perfect, with some significant flaws.\", \"from\": 2011, \"to\": 2206, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 2024 Games\", \"from\": 2011, \"to\": 2025}, {\"ngram\": \"the largest sporting event\", \"from\": 2034, \"to\": 2060}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 2064, \"to\": 2071}, {\"ngram\": \"reusable packaging\", \"from\": 2079, \"to\": 2097}, {\"ngram\": \"thoughrecent reportshave\", \"from\": 2099, \"to\": 2123}, {\"ngram\": \"this effort\", \"from\": 2139, \"to\": 2150}, {\"ngram\": \"some significant flaws\", \"from\": 2183, \"to\": 2205}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A key design requirement of effective reuse systems is that reusable packaging should replace single-use packaging.\", \"from\": 2208, \"to\": 2323, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A key design requirement\", \"from\": 2208, \"to\": 2232}, {\"ngram\": \"effective reuse systems\", \"from\": 2236, \"to\": 2259}, {\"ngram\": \"reusable packaging\", \"from\": 2268, \"to\": 2286}, {\"ngram\": \"single-use packaging\", \"from\": 2302, \"to\": 2322}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is necessary to ensure that the system achieves its objective of maximally reducing packaging waste - and pollution.\", \"from\": 2324, \"to\": 2445, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the system\", \"from\": 2357, \"to\": 2367}, {\"ngram\": \"its objective\", \"from\": 2377, \"to\": 2390}, {\"ngram\": \"packaging waste\", \"from\": 2413, \"to\": 2428}, {\"ngram\": \"pollution\", \"from\": 2435, \"to\": 2444}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To most, this would seem an obvious requirement but unfortunately, at Paris 2024, somewhere in the planning process, this objective got lost or was never prioritised in the first place.\", \"from\": 2446, \"to\": 2631, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an obvious requirement\", \"from\": 2471, \"to\": 2493}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 2516, \"to\": 2521}, {\"ngram\": \"the planning process\", \"from\": 2541, \"to\": 2561}, {\"ngram\": \"this objective\", \"from\": 2563, \"to\": 2577}, {\"ngram\": \"the first place\", \"from\": 2615, \"to\": 2630}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the Paris Games,reports have confirmedthat many of the beverages served to spectators in reusable cups will be poured from single-use plastic bottles.\", \"from\": 2632, \"to\": 2785, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 2635, \"to\": 2650}, {\"ngram\": \"reports\", \"from\": 2651, \"to\": 2658}, {\"ngram\": \"the beverages\", \"from\": 2686, \"to\": 2699}, {\"ngram\": \"spectators\", \"from\": 2710, \"to\": 2720}, {\"ngram\": \"reusable cups\", \"from\": 2724, \"to\": 2737}, {\"ngram\": \"single-use plastic bottles\", \"from\": 2758, \"to\": 2784}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The organisers have claimed that this decision was due to operational restrictions in temporary venues where fountain machines can not be installed.\", \"from\": 2786, \"to\": 2934, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The organisers\", \"from\": 2786, \"to\": 2800}, {\"ngram\": \"this decision\", \"from\": 2819, \"to\": 2832}, {\"ngram\": \"operational restrictions\", \"from\": 2844, \"to\": 2868}, {\"ngram\": \"temporary venues\", \"from\": 2872, \"to\": 2888}, {\"ngram\": \"fountain machines\", \"from\": 2895, \"to\": 2912}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This excuse is hard to swallow.\", \"from\": 2935, \"to\": 2966, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This excuse\", \"from\": 2935, \"to\": 2946}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Leading sponsor Coca-Cola, its packaging and distribution partners, and event organisers should work harder to develop innovative solutions that allow them to meet demand without the need for single-use plastic.\", \"from\": 2967, \"to\": 3178, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2983, \"end\": 2992, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coca-Cola\", \"score\": 0.9999999999295142, \"rank\": 7.060090080687544e-11, \"text\": \"Coca-Cola\", \"types\": [\"Q2095\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coca-Cola\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coca-Cola\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its packaging and distribution partners\", \"from\": 2994, \"to\": 3033}, {\"ngram\": \"event organisers\", \"from\": 3039, \"to\": 3055}, {\"ngram\": \"innovative solutions\", \"from\": 3086, \"to\": 3106}, {\"ngram\": \"demand\", \"from\": 3131, \"to\": 3137}, {\"ngram\": \"the need\", \"from\": 3146, \"to\": 3154}, {\"ngram\": \"single-use plastic\", \"from\": 3159, \"to\": 3177}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An additional key reuse system design requirement is that reusable packaging does not feature attractive event branding.\", \"from\": 3180, \"to\": 3300, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"An additional key reuse system design requirement\", \"from\": 3180, \"to\": 3229}, {\"ngram\": \"reusable packaging\", \"from\": 3238, \"to\": 3256}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unfortunately, at Paris 2024many reusable cups will feature the Olympic logo, making them appeal to spectators as souvenirs and reducing the likelihood they will be returned - and reused.\", \"from\": 3301, \"to\": 3488, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3319, \"end\": 3324, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999877218, \"rank\": 1.2143040117189396e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"2024many\", \"from\": 3325, \"to\": 3333}, {\"ngram\": \"reusable cups\", \"from\": 3334, \"to\": 3347}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic logo\", \"from\": 3361, \"to\": 3377}, {\"ngram\": \"spectators\", \"from\": 3401, \"to\": 3411}, {\"ngram\": \"souvenirs\", \"from\": 3415, \"to\": 3424}, {\"ngram\": \"the likelihood\", \"from\": 3438, \"to\": 3452}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While fans are likely to reuse these cups at home, reuse systems cannot reach their full potential of minimising waste - and carbon emissions - without high return rates.\", \"from\": 3489, \"to\": 3659, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 3495, \"to\": 3499}, {\"ngram\": \"these cups\", \"from\": 3520, \"to\": 3530}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 3534, \"to\": 3538}, {\"ngram\": \"systems\", \"from\": 3546, \"to\": 3553}, {\"ngram\": \"their full potential\", \"from\": 3567, \"to\": 3587}, {\"ngram\": \"waste - and carbon emissions\", \"from\": 3602, \"to\": 3630}, {\"ngram\": \"high return rates\", \"from\": 3641, \"to\": 3658}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Using unbranded reusable cups is completely feasible - these are already being used at large-scale concerts and music festivals such as those owned by the entertainment company Live Nation, where a reusable cup system, TURN, has achieved return rates ofmore than 90 percent.\", \"from\": 3660, \"to\": 3934, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3837, \"end\": 3848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Live_Nation_Entertainment\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.936651612669844e-35, \"text\": \"Live Nation\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Live_Nation_Entertainment\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Live_Nation_Entertainment\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"unbranded reusable cups\", \"from\": 3666, \"to\": 3689}, {\"ngram\": \"large-scale concerts\", \"from\": 3747, \"to\": 3767}, {\"ngram\": \"music festivals\", \"from\": 3772, \"to\": 3787}, {\"ngram\": \"the entertainment company\", \"from\": 3811, \"to\": 3836}, {\"ngram\": \"a reusable cup system\", \"from\": 3856, \"to\": 3877}, {\"ngram\": \"TURN\", \"from\": 3879, \"to\": 3883}, {\"ngram\": \"return rates\", \"from\": 3898, \"to\": 3910}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the flaws, the inclusion of reuse at Paris 2024 remains - for me - a beacon of hope for the oceans.\", \"from\": 3936, \"to\": 4043, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the flaws\", \"from\": 3944, \"to\": 3953}, {\"ngram\": \"the inclusion\", \"from\": 3955, \"to\": 3968}, {\"ngram\": \"reuse\", \"from\": 3972, \"to\": 3977}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 3981, \"to\": 3986}, {\"ngram\": \"hope\", \"from\": 4023, \"to\": 4027}, {\"ngram\": \"the oceans\", \"from\": 4032, \"to\": 4042}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Importantly, with the world watching, Paris 2024 presents an unparalleled opportunity to put the spotlight on reuse, raise awareness about the environmental benefits of reusable packaging, and increase consumer demand for more of it.\", \"from\": 4044, \"to\": 4277, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4082, \"end\": 4092, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1030552200753655e-15, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 4062, \"to\": 4071}, {\"ngram\": \"an unparalleled opportunity\", \"from\": 4102, \"to\": 4129}, {\"ngram\": \"the spotlight\", \"from\": 4137, \"to\": 4150}, {\"ngram\": \"reuse\", \"from\": 4154, \"to\": 4159}, {\"ngram\": \"awareness\", \"from\": 4167, \"to\": 4176}, {\"ngram\": \"the environmental benefits\", \"from\": 4183, \"to\": 4209}, {\"ngram\": \"reusable packaging\", \"from\": 4213, \"to\": 4231}, {\"ngram\": \"consumer demand\", \"from\": 4246, \"to\": 4261}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier this month, more than 100 sport organisations and elite athletes from around the world took advantage of this opportunity,callingon leading beverage companies and sports sponsors to increase reusable packaging in place of single-use plastic.\", \"from\": 4278, \"to\": 4527, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more than 100 sport organisations\", \"from\": 4298, \"to\": 4331}, {\"ngram\": \"elite athletes\", \"from\": 4336, \"to\": 4350}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 4363, \"to\": 4372}, {\"ngram\": \"advantage\", \"from\": 4378, \"to\": 4387}, {\"ngram\": \"this opportunity\", \"from\": 4391, \"to\": 4407}, {\"ngram\": \"callingon leading beverage companies\", \"from\": 4408, \"to\": 4444}, {\"ngram\": \"sports sponsors\", \"from\": 4449, \"to\": 4464}, 